snippet.title: Vexation: Hand Crafted Hell | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam so you know when it's time to take on the ultimate challenge:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2132080/

Vexation is the rage game to end all rage games. Every level is a different genre and art style all packaged within their own little pockets of hand crafted hell.

Website: https://gestmorphgames.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GestmorphG
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gestmorphgames/

The following music was used for this media project:
Music: Jered's Choice by Philip Rice
Free download: https://filmmusic.io/song/6814-jereds-choice
License (CC BY 4.0): https://filmmusic.io/standard-license
Artist website: https://madhominem.com/
